#: _versions/3.6/guides/security-authorize-web-endpoints-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Authorization of web endpoints"
msgstr "Web 端点的授权"

#: _versions/3.6/guides/security-authorize-web-endpoints-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus has an integrated pluggable web security layer.\n"
"If security is enabled, all HTTP requests have a permission check performed to verify that they are allowed to continue.\n"
"Therefore, you cannot use `@PermitAll` to open a path if the path is blocked by the `quarkus.http.auth.` configuration."
msgstr "Quarkus 集成了可插拔的网络安全层。如果启用了安全层，所有 HTTP 请求都要进行权限检查，以确认是否允许继续。因此，如果 `quarkus.http.auth.` 配置阻止了路径，就不能使用 `@PermitAll` 打开路径。"

#: _versions/3.6/guides/security-authorize-web-endpoints-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you use Jakarta RESTful Web Services, consider using `quarkus.security.jaxrs.deny-unannotated-endpoints` or `quarkus.security.jaxrs.default-roles-allowed` to set default security requirements instead of HTTP path-level matching because annotations can override these properties on an individual endpoint."
msgstr "如果您使用 JAX-RS，请考虑使用 `quarkus.security.jaxrs.deny-unannotated-endpoints` 或 `quarkus.security.jaxrs.default-roles-allowed` 来设置默认的安全要求，而不是 HTTP 路径级别的匹配，因为注释可以在单个端点上覆盖这些属性。"

#: _versions/3.6/guides/security-authorize-web-endpoints-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Authorization is based on user roles that the security provider provides.\n"
"To customize these roles, a `SecurityIdentityAugmentor` can be created, see\n"
"xref:security-customization.adoc#security-identity-customization[Security Identity Customization]."
msgstr "授权基于安全提供商提供的用户角色。若要自定义这些角色，可以创建 `一个 SecurityIdentityAugmentor` ，请参阅 xref:security-customization.adoc#security-identity-customization[“安全身份自定义”] 。"

